WEBVTT

00:00:09.822 --> 00:00:19.081 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
God is love, and he invites us:
‘Walk with me and love my way.’

00:00:19.081 --> 00:00:28.382 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When we love both God and neighbor,
Gracious deeds will fill each day.

00:00:28.382 --> 00:00:37.933 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Therein lies the key to living;
Therein lies the life we seek.

00:00:38.767 --> 00:00:49.778 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Christlike love will never fail us;
Christlike love through us will speak.

00:00:52.573 --> 00:01:01.457 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Love of truth moves us to action;
Love of God moves us to love.

00:01:01.457 --> 00:01:10.674 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When we fail he seeks to help us;
By his strength we rise above.

00:01:10.674 --> 00:01:21.143 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Love is pure and never jealous;
Love is kind and bears all things.

00:01:21.143 --> 00:01:32.154 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
May we grow to love our brother;
May we taste what true love brings.

00:01:34.698 --> 00:01:43.999 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Never let resentment lead you;
May it never take your hand.

00:01:43.999 --> 00:01:53.175 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Look to God, and he will guide you;
He will teach you these commands:

00:01:53.175 --> 00:02:03.727 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Love of God and love of neighbor,
Ev’rything that love should be.

00:02:03.727 --> 00:02:17.741 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
May we always show to others
Godlike love, yes, tenderly.

